    import sys

sys.path.append("../../../")

from random import sample
import numpy as np
from utils.plot import plot
from utils.dataset import LMDBImageReader

reader = LMDBImageReader("../../../output/brixia/lmdb")
indices = sample(list(range(reader.get_length())), 25)
print("Dataset Length:", reader.get_length())
plot([[np.array(reader.get_img((indices[j * 5 + i]))) for i in range(5)] for j in range(5)])
